data.description: Unique property in O'neals! 3 bedroom, 2 1/2 bath plus office with separate entrance. Large kitchen with farmhouse sink, built in wine fridge, and walk in pantry. Spacious primary bedroom with over sized custom built closet.10 acres with recently graded additional building spot for large shop or second home. Two addresses associated with the property so could easily add an ADU. Lewis creek runs through property. Owned 500 gallon propane tank, commercial septic, two wells with 5000 gallon storage tank. RV parking and hook up. 220 power in shop. Outdoor bathroom off the deck for entertaining. Irrigated landscape. Large shed for storage. Automatic gate at entrance. 40 minutes to Fresno, 10 minutes to Bass Lake. Too many amenities to list, come see for yourself today!
